title: Jason Biggs' wife Jenny Mollen deletes bathroom selfie after accidentally revealing his genitals
text:
Outrage over Jason Biggs Malaysia Airlines crash joke 
A bathroom prank photo posted online by actor Jason Biggs' social media-loving wife Jenny Mollen has backfired on the couple. 
Mollen posed for a selfie as the naked American Pie star squatted on a toilet behind her, a magazine covering his genitals. 
But Biggs' manhood wasn't completely out of sight in the Instagram picture - Mollen's quirky shot captured his genitals hanging beneath the mag. 
Fans mused whether the big reveal was intentional until Mollen pulled the picture from social media, suggesting she didn't spot her man's testicles at first. Sponsored Links
